content.text:
Project utilizing the 'StreamSync' framework for interactive use of BarentsWatch and Frost APIs. The
 project is a part of the course 'IND320' at NMBU. The web app allows the user to download and
 explore data, in addition to some simple interactive forecasting.

__IMPORTANT__

* To run locally, modify the API credentials at the top of the 'functions.fetching'-file.
* Must have Cassandra running locally.
